name: The Congregation
description:
"The Congregation" is about the powerful arrangement of four planets in Capricorn: Mars, Venus, Mercury, and Pluto, soon to be joined by the Moon. Capricorn reflects productivity, hard work, and determination, but also foundations, roots, and preservation. These planets together indicate the powerful and profound concentration on the things we want to achieve, create, but also cherish and protect.

All proceeds from the primary sale of this work go to BRG.exe for the #ORBS4BRG event.
